snippet.title: Ulta Haul 2020 | ALL NEW Drugstore Makeup | Sincerely Amber Marie Mack
snippet.description:
Hey everyone! Welcome back to my channel! I'm back with another video. Due to the unfortunate events last week I did not feel in my heart it was appropriate to post. Rest in Peace Kobe and Gigi Bryant 💜💛. Its time to put the Mamba Mentality to work! This is my first 2020 Ulta Haul of the year. (trust me there will be more)! I got to pick up some pretty bomb items in the drugstore and can't wait to share! I hope you enjoy! Thanks for watching and don’t forget to LIKE, SUBSCRIBE, SHARE, and COMMENT! See you in my next video!
